        "title": "In CrafterCMS, RTE deletes some html tags without inner text",
        "body": "<p>In <strong>CrafterCMS<\/strong>, in a content type, I have a field type <strong>RTE<\/strong>,<\/p>\n\n<p>If I use the source option and write following code:<\/p>\n\n<pre><code>&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;Test&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;div class=\"item_icon\"&gt;&lt;i class=\"fa fa-location-arrow\"&gt;&lt;/i&gt;&lt;/div&gt;\n<\/code><\/pre>\n\n<p>after update it and be back the code is <\/p>\n\n<pre><code>&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;Test&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\n<\/code><\/pre>\n\n<p>(last part was deleted)<\/p>\n\n<p>Is this the expected behavior? can it be changed by configuration?<\/p>\n",
