        "body": "<p>The Crafter team is working on an upgrade of TinyMCE in Crafter CMS 3.0, see here: <a href=\"https://github.com/craftercms/craftercms/issues/793\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\">https://github.com/craftercms/craftercms/issues/793<\/a><\/p>\n\n<p>If you need a fix right away, you can try to use \"&amp;nbsp\", or use a tag with: \"display:none\" for example: <code>&lt;span style=\"display:none\"&gt;Something&lt;/span&gt;<\/code><\/p>\n",
